<section class=3D"class-description" id=3D"class-description">
<dl class=3D"notes">
<dt>All Implemented Interfaces:</dt>
<dd><code><a href=3D"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/io/Seri=
alizable.html" title=3D"class or interface in java.io" class=3D"external-li=
